MEDIA personality Minnie Dlamini-Jones has revealed her baby’s gender. The Homeground presenter shared a picture from her baby shower yesterday and captioned it: “It’s a boy.” Reality TV star, Shauwn Mkhize, also attended the baby shower and shared some snaps of the event. She also mentioned that she is the god mother to Minnie’s child on the post. Minnie announced her pregnancy last month on her husband Quinton’s birthday, saying it was a gift to him. ALSO READ | SELLO MAAKE KA-NCUBE: THERE IS NO SUCH THING AS RETIRING IN ACTING Since then, the mum-to-be has since been posting updates about her pregnancy on social media. Last week she said the doctor advised her not to fly, so she took a road trip to Durban. The couple, that wedded in 2017, finally fell pregnant after people on social media and media reports had said she was pregnant many times over the past years when she wasn’t. It’s a boy ?? #BecomingMamaJones A post shared by  Minnie (@minniedlamini) on Oct 10, 2020 at 8:51am PDT 